description:
Chad and Alta Dillard vanished along with a friend from a street corner in the French Quarter of New Orleans, what follows was missing time, Entity encounters, unbelievable experiences and a face to face with a shape-shifter.

This is the one of a kind tale of 3 people and the night their lives took a terrifying journey straight to the heart of the Twilight Zone.

Plus a brand new Theater of the Mind
